game.name: Xtreme Sky Car Parking
game.description:
All the crazy gamers have already reached out here to enjoy the realistic parking experience. Where are you, friends? Join Xtreme Sky Car Parking and be prepared to park your vehicle on the designated spot in the sky of the awesome city! Wow! There are multiple driving missions to take care of you in this brand new racing challenge. Complete each level, earn points and unlock new car models later! The city is full of obstacles and other vehicles to deal with.

You of course have to use your skill to park your assigned vehicle without being crashed with other cars. People living in a large metropolis find difficulty in car parking. Today we have got you covered with a cool HTML5 parking game where you are going to help different people put their cars in certain places. Keep your eyes on the screen to find out the special arrows which will guide you to drive your vehicle to a specific place!

Do try to be in a hurry as you have to park your vehicle in the allotted lines to earn points! The points you earn will also help you further to buy new car models to be parked. There are various obstacles, elevators, hard ways, and gates to explore in this cool car parking simulator. Buttons, steering wheel and gyroscope are the three types of controls you use. Try out other free parking simulators on atmegame.com and improve your driving abilities to the maximum! You are just a few clicks away from the supersport car driving experience.
